title: Herby Halloumi & Garlic Rice with Cucumber Salsa & Tangy Yoghurt Drizzle
description: Get ready for a flavour-packed feast! Meet our pre-marinated haloumi, juicy and delicious. Pair them with fragrant garlic rice, a refreshing cucumber salsa and a creamy garlic yogurt drizzle for the perfect balance of zest, crunch and richness!
